{"id": "1231461662968774727", "channel_id": "1231443738996244523", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "說得很清楚全面，也沒什麼大的問題，給薯條。", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:28:59.903000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231443738996244523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一个萌新向的抽卡和常见问题攻略…", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1231462185411280927", "channel_id": "1231443738996244523", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "關於2(a)，我想補充一下，不建議玩御四家開荒，遊戲進度會慢不少。\n無限定的話，速度而言，只建議莉茲開荒，盡快打通主線開滿各種功能會大大提升養成速度。", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:31:04.463000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-21T06:44:12.141000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231443738996244523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一个萌新向的抽卡和常见问题攻略…", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1231462714954747937", "channel_id": "1231443738996244523", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "並且玩到中期會需要練很多隊伍、很多角色，因此不太存在為了屯資源而克難的情況，且大部分角色都能養都能玩。", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:33:10.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:36:04.301000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231443738996244523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一个萌新向的抽卡和常见问题攻略…", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1231466676055179314", "channel_id": "1231443738996244523", "type": 19, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "莉茲開荒到第五章後 就可以去玩心儀的隊伍了 因此就算真的不喜歡莉茲 也不太會浪費什麼養成材料 並且隊伍內的成員也都算實用", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:48:55.116000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-21T04:49:24.535000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1231462185411280927", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231443738996244523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一个萌新向的抽卡和常见问题攻略…", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1231488159167025152", "channel_id": "1231443738996244523", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "补充几个讯息：\n\n1.楼主讲的非常全面，很赞。\n\n2.关于初始4人：使用他们开荒，相比于T0队伍会有一定的难度，但不会差太多。\n\n使用初始4人的好处在于，他们能够训练新手玩家最基础的战斗意识与技巧，对于打好这个游戏的基本功有着非常大的帮助。\n\n3：玩莉兹队需要学习一个基本意识：莉兹需要力量才能打出伤害，而不是更多的绿炎才能打出伤害", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T06:14:17.089000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231443738996244523", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一个萌新向的抽卡和常见问题攻略…", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130"]}
