{"id": "1231624362831118418", "channel_id": "1230861300926779404", "type": 0, "author_id": "1221463356138061828", "author_name": "lilisi123456", "author_bot": false, "content": "刻印方面，给小小心意（艾继丝三启）和苍白回旋有奇效，因为两者的回手频率超高，可以非常快速的积累灵感，灵感则可以用来弥补算力的问题，更重要的是，灵感可以用来控牌序，保证小小心愿和苍白长时间处于弃牌堆", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T15:15:30.573000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1230861300926779404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿格里帕（蜘蛛）食用指南", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1231547668216549376", "channel_id": "1226792395249811456", "type": 0, "author_id": "1132713962299998248", "author_name": "henry.0701", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/JrPn6EySdnE\n嘗試把自己對神父的解讀壓在4分鐘\nuid:100050347", "timestamp": "2024-04-21T10:10:45.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-21T10:13:46.606000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "【忘卻前夜】用4分鐘了解神父 薩爾瓦多全面解析", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JrPn6EySdnE", "description": "#忘卻前夜  #忘卻前夜攻略   #彌薩格大學攻略募集四期 #薩爾瓦多\n這次來解析為了弟兄姊妹的神父！\n這次嘗試盡可能壓縮影片時長！(上傳之後居然多1秒！)\n如果有什麼問題或是遺漏的地方可以留言跟恆燐說！\n\nBGM： [FREE BGM] ‘Once Upon a Time’ / Relaxing Fantasy Game Style Cozy Music 30M for Study\n\n章節： \n00:00 開頭 \n00:07 簡介\n00:29 技能\n00:41 啟靈\n00:56 密契\n01:03 命輪推薦\n01:43 抽取建議\n02:13 隊伍推薦\n03:48 結束"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1226792395249811456", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💌「薩爾瓦多」體驗交流分享活動💌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
